1022
00:51:06,431 --> 00:51:08,097
Yeah, go ahead.
Please, please do.

1023
00:51:08,099 --> 00:51:10,099
Is it, uh...

1024
00:51:10,101 --> 00:51:13,436
Wow, it's--wow, it is
