1106
00:56:32,590 --> 00:56:35,157
being handed the trophy
and remember thinking

1107
00:56:35,159 --> 00:56:37,760
"please don't drop it,
you're on national television.

1108
00:56:37,762 --> 00:56:39,762
You got millions
of people watching."

1109
00:56:39,764 --> 00:56:41,096
So I think I held it
with two hands,

1110
00:56:41,098 --> 00:56:42,564
but it's really
not very heavy at all.

1111
00:56:42,566 --> 00:56:43,966
But it is--it is beautiful

1112
00:56:43,968 --> 00:56:46,935
and, uh, we sure like
the four that we have

