to achieve

1114
00:56:50,574 --> 00:56:53,142
'cause there are 31
other clubs out there
trying to do the same thing.

1115
00:56:53,144 --> 00:56:54,977
By the time
the trophy is coming out,

1116
00:56:54,979 --> 00:56:57,646
usually we're, like,
divvying up, you know,

1117
00:56:57,648 --> 00:56:59,782
our winnings or our losses

1118
00:56:59,784 --> 00:57:01,950
and not paying
a lot of attention

1119
00:57:01,952 --> 00:57:04,953
to that super bowl trophy,
but I bet the players are.

