01:00:20,884 --> 01:00:22,317
to represent the sky--

1151
01:00:22,319 --> 01:00:24,319
that there may
be a correlation.

1152
01:00:24,321 --> 01:00:26,955
It's one we're perfectly
willing to accept.

1153
01:00:26,957 --> 01:00:29,992
It's all surrounded
by the world's largest,

1154
01:00:29,994 --> 01:00:33,161
most magnificent piece
of Tiffany glass,

1155
01:00:33,163 --> 01:00:36,832
the clock, that just
identifies this terminal.

1156
01:00:46,009 --> 01:00:48,176
